4/14(Thu.) How technology has changed our lives? / The second session is the table topic.(Host: William)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:35 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:35-9:00 pm Debate<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />--------------------------------------------<br /><br />Session I : How technology has changed our lives?<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/SE4g9vbik7w">https://youtu.be/SE4g9vbik7w</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/0hlexbccHjo">https://youtu.be/0hlexbccHjo</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. How does technology impact your daily life?<br />2. How has technology changed the way we read books? <br />3. How can technology help us achieve our goals? <br />4. Can you learn tech skills at home? <br />5. What is the negative effects of technology?<br /><br />--------------------------------------------<br /><br />Session 2: The second session is the table topic .<br /><br />Each member prepares some questions. <br /><br />In the sub-group members can take turns to ask and answer the questions to each other.<br /><br />During the presentation members  ask the questions and others answer the asking questions.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=46353">Ellen Lu</a> — Sat Apr 09, 2022 10:34 am</p><hr />
